I"C<p>Our agency sponsors a local cycling event and I used the opportunity to film and produce a promotional video for it using my Sony RX100 IV, GoPro and DJI Phantom 4 drone.</p>

<p>The film combines a range of handheld, car-mounted and aerial footage of the event. I edited the film using Adobe Premiere Pro and used Adobe After Effects to create the animated route maps to draw a path of the route.</p>

